ance/realtime/article/20170530/5675</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:50:58.000Z","msg":"幾年前舊登扮日本人開嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"唔怪得咁熟口面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2359c6346e9d754f046cf534f039ab5adc4f1e","tid":977332,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a24cfaca4446c6a865173ff5d511a3972c24841","tid":977332,"uid":12013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28a47deaebafe30ebff55e004b3c95050bf2b0a","tid":977332,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2a0730c95ceac14cd1695df9cc950299202803","tid":977332,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c9330ea918e1130b9e6f9cb7ddd039dc6891a4","tid":977332,"uid":11703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"240459602046dd9d62538b5be190f6dc212831f4","tid":977332,"uid":123264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5e12067e864ddf8eec8c0e33c726bebe0f7c04f2","tid":977332,"uid":11703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"香港啲營商環境根本就唔撚掂<br />\n畀舖租搞死晒<br />\n最近咩要環保走飲管根本晒氣<br />\n香港人啲環保意識大家心照喇<br />\n根本就係要慳成本<br />\n可以諗下連飲管呢啲成本都要咁執著<br />\n其他更重要嘅嘢有得cut都cut晒<br />\n低人工又令員工士氣差<br />\n邊會做得好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:44:25.000Z","msg":"香港最大問題就係呢個假既市場 根本唔係以食物同服務質素決定價錢 而係由地產商玩哂<br />\n中國人商家mindset做生意得一個字cut cost<br />\n做窮人連食垃圾同屎都要比人管<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環保撚最叻係管窮人 有錢佬同商家平時點浪費係唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果係呢度呻下又比傻仔話踩港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班傻仔咁中意香港 就咪撚成日話移民移民啦 同埋仲搞咩香港獨立搞埋革命 香港咁撚好駛咩革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:24:59.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n中國人淨係識cut cost<br />\n以餐廳為例<br />\n日本人遇上逆境好少首先諗cut cost<br />\n反而會不斷諗方法改革<br />\n例如會諗新menu吸新客<br />\n未必有效，可能仲會諗埋啲on9嘢<br />\n但我覺得點都好過中國人淨係識cut cost減人工<br />\n你死你賤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"九十年代經濟衰退<br />\n經團連第一個跳出黎叫啲公司cut福利cut人件費，所以先搞到今日咁多派遣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9f42eec4f2dc00d5d1a6588beb48fa8e0eb0d4","tid":977332,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6efd211d5acc45c6fbe0a92970744c00c0bda1f","tid":977332,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aab8427215a58d13a78f84c3c84d5a623442b2a7","tid":977332,"uid":72581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:41:32.000Z","msg":"做緊主婦 好開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"我家姐都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打老公係日本人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:45:34.000Z","msg":"唔係呀，contract工<br />\n住左一年，打算住多2-3年"},{"pid":"d78bf30807750b67fca5e3c051608faac7d6f402","tid":977332,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d9f42eec4f2dc00d5d1a6588beb48fa8e0eb0d4","tid":977332,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6efd211d5acc45c6fbe0a92970744c00c0bda1f","tid":977332,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dis